{"word":"G2002 - ἐπισωρεύω - episōreúō - ep-ee-so-ryoo'-o - Heap","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπισωρεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">episōreúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-so-ryoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Heap</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திரளாகச்சேர்"},{"paragraph":"to heap up, accumulate in piles"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4987 - σωρεύω - sōreúō - sore-yoo'-o/4987\">G4987</a>; to <i>accumulate further</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>seek</i> additionally: - heap.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2002/2002\">G2002</a>, <a href=\"#/G4987/4987\">G4987</a>"}]}